These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, spanish, polish, colombian, british, brazilian, australian
1. the spanish is in the middle##1
2. the spanish is on the left of the polish##1
3. the british is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the russian is on the right of the polish##1
5. the australian is on the far left##1
6. the brazilian is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | australian | colombian | british | spanish | polish | russian | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  social-worker, bartender, videographer, pilot, accountant, lawyer, musician
1. the musician is on the far right##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1
3. the social-worker is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the accountant is on the left of the videographer##1
5. the pilot is on the right of the lawyer##1
6. the musician is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | social-worker | accountant | videographer | lawyer | pilot | bartender | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, traveling, reading, photography, collecting, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | photography | cooking | collecting | traveling | gardening | dancing | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
