1. the dutch is on the far left##1
2. the french is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the russian is on the far right##1
4. the malaysian is on the left of the russian##1
5. the colombian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7    |
| Nationality   | dutch | french | japanese | colombian | american | malaysian | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, bird, horse, frog, hamster, dog
1. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | dog | bird | horse | hamster | rabbit | rat | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-6::.
