.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-7::.
There 7 different types of food: strawberry, artichoke, cherry, corn, cauliflower, asparagus, pear
1. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person eating pear is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |     7      |
| Food   | corn | asparagus | cauliflower | pear | strawberry | artichoke | cherry |

