.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: romance, action, time-travel, western, musical, zombie, epic
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | action | romance | zombie | western | epic | time-travel |

 #################################

 
